name: Element_getElementByIdTest
description: Unit tests for the getElementById method of the Element class in Jsoup.

test_cases.name: testGetElementById_ExistingId
test_cases.description: Tests the getElementById method with an existing ID, ensuring the correct element is retrieved and its properties are as expected.

test_cases.name: testGetElementById_NonExistingId
test_cases.description: Tests the getElementById method with a non-existing ID, ensuring null is returned.

test_cases.name: testGetElementById_EmptyId
test_cases.description: Tests the getElementById method with an empty ID, ensuring an IllegalArgumentException is thrown.

test_cases.name: testGetElementById_NullId
test_cases.description: Tests the getElementById method with a null ID, ensuring an IllegalArgumentException is thrown.
